{"tid":146200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"樂天超市大陸關4家店後 其他多家店也遭以消防檢查之名臨時查封","createTime":"2017-03-07T01:25:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T05:18:21.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3d5c2e71de0acfc7b0b7247cb5371aa8c70f2005","tid":146200,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T01:25:33.000Z","msg":"（中央社台北6日電）南韓樂天集團捲入中韓之間的終端高空防衛系統（THAAD）部署爭議後，已有江蘇常州和遼寧丹東4家超市關閉，其他多家店也以消防檢查之名陸續遭「臨時查封」。<br />\n<br />\n路透社今天報導，樂天集團發言人6日表示，樂天瑪特在中國大陸遼寧丹東、江蘇常州和其他兩個地方的4家超市被檢查後關閉了，並未透露原因。今年1月份統計資料顯示，樂天瑪特超市在中國大陸還有115家店。<br />\n<br />\n而根據新華網，安徽淮南的樂天超市也因消防整治被臨時查封，這一波被檢查的還有其他企業。安徽官方稱，這是為了吸取2月5日這將天台重大火災教訓所做的專項治理，但網友留言中不乏認為這是「把執法作為打擊工具」。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，樂天是南韓第5大企業，中國大陸是其最大海外市場，自1994年進軍中國市場以來，樂天在大陸市場已覆蓋零售、旅遊、石化、金融、製造、食品、建設、服務等多個領域。1060306"},{"pid":"4ae5c272f37153b7650b57ce443b241027cdd50a","tid":146200,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T11:47:46.000Z","msg":"唔好泛政治化呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27076ce17ef664a5bb7b424c1bf7f09c5a39c503","tid":146200,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T11:49:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好泛政治化呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cc6352e15a33396abb6a7594f0ed5fc75f8f1c0","tid":146200,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T12:15:33.000Z","msg":"投資咁多係大陸就抵佢hum家鏟啦"},{"pid":"08211fa64ec0f5e6d03917d71d3a0b58026db15d","tid":146200,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T20:36:01.000Z","msg":"支那搞唔掂人地國家就搞人地生意，仲大大聲話依法治國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022f1646a9d2c7aaa24c70f929f37a66574d02f6","tid":146200,"uid":28599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T20:46:01.000Z","msg":"歡迎外資投資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以後搵鬼投資咩"},{"pid":"06706bcc8ccabcfc59e77ef3b505e46f71a800c8","tid":146200,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T02:47:37.000Z","msg":"做得好 支那狗"},{"pid":"63b47e62662fe35c77001261edb6915a7bd7f65b","tid":146200,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T02:54:29.000Z","msg":"錢又唔俾拎走，又用國家權力搞人地做生意<br />\n究竟支那幾時仆街爆煲，我想睇會變成點<br />\n仲"},{"pid":"7e452a9e02c306639d62207cac37c6e10b315224","tid":146200,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T03:02:58.000Z","msg":"支狗vs泡狗 場戲幾好睇<br />\n幾時到泡狗出招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0419ec3c8753ace4b6714f60110b60be7f199ec7","tid":146200,"uid":2450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T03:22:12.000Z","msg":"幾時抵制美國佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a3d2ca300ba5ce8c6fc465f8c7f530995e8b63","tid":146200,"uid":77518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T03:26:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"110c28124e37d77dbc26d7d6e3445e5abfa49748","tid":146200,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T03:30:10.000Z","msg":"佢咁做咪姐係叫強國人快d去未執既鋪頭清貨,你都個強國人身體有幾誠實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8f2b52d33d7187d6478010783084cf906c0c827","tid":146200,"uid":4241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T03:30:51.00